gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 128, Cavaliers 120
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Shai Gilgeous-Alexanders 43 points (15-22 FG), seven rebounds, and six assists, the Thunder defeated the Cavaliers, 128-120. Chet Holmgren added 15 points (7-10 FG), seven rebounds, and three blocks for the Thunder in the victory, while Caris LeVert tallied 29 points, five rebounds, and five assists for the Cavaliers in the losing effort. The Thunder improve to 5-3 on the season, while the Cavaliers fall to 3-5.
